### Setup Vercel Analytics script in HTML

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/analytics/custom-events

Initializes Vercel Analytics in vanilla HTML by adding a script that defines the window.va function and loads the Vercel insights script. Place this before any other scripts that use the va function.

```html
<script>
  window.va =
    window.va ||
    function () {
      (window.vaq = window.vaq || []).push(arguments);
    };
</script>
{/* Place it above this script tag when already added */}
<script defer src="/_vercel/insights/script.js"></script>
```

