### Configure Microfrontends Proxy Script in package.json

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/llms-full

Set up a proxy script in package.json for local development when not using Turborepo. This script enables the @vercel/microfrontends local development proxy to route requests to your local microfrontend application.

```json
"scripts": {
  "proxy": "microfrontends proxy --local-apps my-local-app-name"
}
```

