### Configure Microfrontends Proxy Script in package.json

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/microfrontends/quickstart

Add a proxy script to package.json to start the local development proxy for microfrontends without Turborepo. This script runs the microfrontends proxy and specifies which local app to use. The proxy automatically routes requests to your local application during development.

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "proxy": "microfrontends proxy --local-apps my-local-app-name"
  }
}
```

