### Initialize BotID in SvelteKit Client Hooks

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/botid/get-started

Configure BotID protection in SvelteKit's client-side hooks file. Exports an init function that calls initBotId() to protect specified API routes.

```typescript
import { initBotId } from 'botid/client/core';

export function init() {
  initBotId({
    protect: [
      {
        path: '/api/post-data',
        method: 'POST',
      },
    ],
  });
}
```

```javascript
import { initBotId } from 'botid/client/core';

export function init() {
  initBotId({
    protect: [
      {
        path: '/api/post-data',
        method: 'POST',
      },
    ],
  });
}
```

