### Disable Build Cache in Deploy Hook Request

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/deploy-hooks

Append the query parameter `?buildCache=false` to a Deploy Hook URL to skip using cached build artifacts. This forces a fresh build but increases build time compared to using the default caching behavior.

```bash
curl -X POST https://api.vercel.com/v1/integrations/deploy/prj_98g22o5YUFVHlKOzj9vKPTyN2SDG/tKybBxqhQs?buildCache=false
```

