### Add Type-Check Script to package.json

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/llms-full

This `package.json` snippet demonstrates adding a `type-check` script to a project's `scripts` section. The script uses `tsc -p tsconfig.json --noEmit` to run TypeScript type checking based on the project's `tsconfig.json` without emitting any JavaScript files, ensuring only type validation occurs.

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    ...,
    "type-check": "tsc -p tsconfig.json --noEmit"
  }
}
```

