### Trigger Deploy Hook with cURL POST Request

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/deploy-hooks

Send a POST request to a Deploy Hook URL to trigger a deployment. The request does not require authentication headers or payload body. The response returns a job object with deployment status information.

```bash
curl -X POST https://api.vercel.com/v1/integrations/deploy/prj_98g22o5YUFVHlKOzj9vKPTyN2SDG/tKybBxqhQs
```

