### Trigger Deployment with Deploy Hooks HTTP Request

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/llms-full

Make an HTTP GET or POST request to a Deploy Hook URL to trigger a deployment on Vercel. Deploy Hooks require a connected Git repository but do not require a new commit to execute. The unique URL is generated from Project settings.

```http
GET|POST <unique-deploy-hook-url>
```

