### Add Type Check Script to package.json (JSON)

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/conformance/rules/TYPESCRIPT_CONFIGURATION

Shows how to add a `type-check` script to the `scripts` section of `package.json`, enabling type checking using `tsc` for the project's `tsconfig.json` without emitting any output files. This script is crucial for integrating type safety checks into development and CI/CD workflows.

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "...",
    "type-check": "tsc -p tsconfig.json --noEmit"
  }
}
```

