### Filter Analytics Events with beforeSend in SvelteKit (JavaScript)

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/analytics/redacting-sensitive-data

Configures event filtering in SvelteKit using JavaScript with injectAnalytics. The beforeSend callback filters private URLs from analytics tracking. Dependencies: @vercel/analytics/sveltekit.

```javascript
import { injectAnalytics } from '@vercel/analytics/sveltekit';

injectAnalytics({
  beforeSend(event) {
    if (event.url.includes('/private')) {
      return null;
    }
    return event;
  },
});
```

