### Execute build script in Python

Source: https://vercel.com/docs/frameworks/backend/fastapi

Implement a custom build script that performs pre-deployment tasks. This script runs during the build phase on Vercel and can be used for tasks like generating configuration files or compiling assets.

```python
def main():
    print("Running build command...")
    with open("build.txt", "w") as f:
        f.write("BUILD_COMMAND")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
```

